Dorycnium 
<normalizedToken id="D66F38CA6587C7C53AC4A92DF62EDADC" originalValue="germánicum" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">germanicum</normalizedToken>
(Gremli) Rikli
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="DFA2A19C409A1B90B1281BE2533F76D6" pageId="null" pageNumber="538" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="3082AF2905E6E0797F3DF011CCABCF76" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Deutscher Backenklee</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="0BB772988487BFC873349AE5A08F0A2A" pageId="null" pageNumber="538" type="description">
<paragraph id="FAC6D050C7C143953AC415153D60C4CD" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="AC37A750D610CAAE93D6B387D3DBAA70" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Dorycnium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="538" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="herbaceum">
<emphasis id="DE1C7846AFDEF59A6ACB9B789347C0B2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">D. herbaceum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2) durch folgende Merkmale: 15-45 cm hoch; 
<emphasis id="BF3E17765761F1A14D70AD643702EFA8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
<normalizedToken id="54C676E0A064F31AB0E6282995D8B6C2" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
dicht anliegend behaart; 
<normalizedToken id="BD25203CE3E2645B47FF343BD49C391E" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
4-8mal so lang wie breit; 
<normalizedToken id="9C7E88B878BECB110EECFCD6B6F5CC3C" originalValue="Blütenstände" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Bluetenstaende</normalizedToken>
8-15 
<normalizedToken id="99F10295000629E6C031FB764A6FFC0A" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">bluetig</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="9879B3022887B0B11E3FA027D12887A6" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
1,5-2 mm lang; 
<emphasis id="41379CDF8AA0E193DC2A8F5062B9326F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
Kelch 2,5-3,5 mm lang; Kelchzipfel etwa so lang wie die 
<normalizedToken id="886C8345A295EDC5F753441B33356527" originalValue="Kelchröhre" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Kelchroehre</normalizedToken>
; Krone 5-7 mm lang. -
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="117220F1BCD8F0F8030504A6D14C8342" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B977F3FEDD0DDE893E5FBB86F60388B6" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
<emphasis id="1BCFA78945AD67EB4C007866B17EFCD2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="9610F7214B98E00B0A4E0FB4D9D58700" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">14:</emphasis>
Material aus botanischen 
<normalizedToken id="2D6CC2278E0A238B5A628FABA1F07A72" originalValue="Gärten" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Gaerten</normalizedToken>
(Tschechow und Kartashova 1932).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B9D7E781809FDA179AD8073527DC7E17" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
<emphasis id="E70B6C407276F9423B1669709B240E6B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, selten montan. 
<normalizedToken id="EE67621AE2A14D9812D62EC65513F6E6" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="683CFCDDFF53F2D618F3B2F3DDEB0933" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Dorycnium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="538" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="herbaceum">
<emphasis id="3615483EA2A1108BABCA3562637D4867" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">D. herbaceum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 2).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="52F3F99EFCB0E475DCBCCFB596A876E2" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
<emphasis id="49A6EBAF60A1206F1795AC743EAD759B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="2C9EEC1C56B0E5C80DDB462112622BF0" originalValue="Südosteuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Suedosteuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
Ostalpen, 
<normalizedToken id="2DFAA58F2B34343C056A7D3590A4BF4C" originalValue="Südpolen" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Suedpolen</normalizedToken>
, Donaubecken, Balkanhalbinsel. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel et al. (1965). - Im Gebiet: Rheintal (zwischen Chur und Luziensteig), Walgau im Vorarlberg (zwischen 
<normalizedToken id="61A19AB6AF8B770D88C1E1D3A2ABBA35" originalValue="Göfis" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">Goefis</normalizedToken>
und Braz), Montafon, Oberinntal (von Landeck an 
<normalizedToken id="C6A7593DC723F6DAFEEEA420CC046290" originalValue="abwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">abwaerts</normalizedToken>
), 
<normalizedToken id="705445BAA8185B34E0083C8D8D64E731" originalValue="südliches" pageId="null" pageNumber="538">suedliches</normalizedToken>
Tessin (Lugano, Meride) Comerseegebiet (Canzo).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
